      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxk15huggafx5d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 915,
      "y": 145,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "text": "Block B pixels\nnear boundary:\n~140, 141, 142",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxkgqf2pcbcylo",
      "type": "line",
      "x": 897,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 0,
      "height": 130,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxkzclhw8z4z9o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 868,
      "y": 248,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "text": "visible JUMP\n~20 pixel values!",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxk9lirtduu20e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 275,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "The reconstructed image has sudden brightness jumps at every 8-pixel boundary —",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxkoxau7z3bel",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 295,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "this is the 'blocking artifact'. The DCT basis functions are localized to each block,",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxktv2ah649bmb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 315,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "text": "so quantizing them independently creates discontinuities at block edges.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxkhrz8p2or3z",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 1020,
      "height": 65,
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxkwwijhpxpsdc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 45,
      "y": 355,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "text": "LEARNED SOLUTION: Nonlinear transform g_a processes the WHOLE image (not blocks).",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxks82gw29itvf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 45,
      "y": 378,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Ballé et al.: 'our method appears to progressively simplify contours... effectively concealing the underlying quantization'",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mnvqotxkniz1r00x4qb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 450,
      "y": 248,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": "no block boundaries\nbetween A and B\nto cause artifacts",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:28:03.854Z",
      "version": 1
    }
  ],
